Title: Man who dragged woman into laneway may avoid prison, court hears
Summary: A man cleared of intending to sexually assault a woman he dragged into a city laneway may avoid prison on a lesser charge, a court has heard.

Title: Ex-northern beaches teacher arrested for historical sexual assault of student
Summary: The 67-year-old woman is accused of abusing a student at Beacon Hill High School from 1978 to 1980.

Title: Charges against Mildura pair dropped over neighbours Aboriginal flag dispute
Summary: Criminal charges against a Mildura pair filmed trying to tear down an Aboriginal flag and questioning their neighbours Indigenous identity have been dropped.

Title: Least worst option as sex assault survivors win right to speak
Summary: Survivors of rape and sexual assault will be able to publicly identify themselves after an emotional night in Parliament.

Title: One arrest leads to discovery of global online paedophile network
Summary: During the operation, police uncovered what is believed to be an extensive online paedophile network used to share photos and videos of child abuse.

Title: Woman charged after alleged Valley bus incident left man with puncture wound
Summary: Police had said initial investigations suggested the man was allegedly confronted while exiting the bus near the corner of Brunswick and Robertson streets on Monday.

Title: Crime scene declared after suspicious fire at Gold Coast brothel
Summary: Police are investigating the fire that occurred in the early hours of Tuesday morning.

Title: NSW proposes new laws to recognise pregnancies lost as result of crime
Summary: The proposal has angered some Coalition MPs because it does not create a separate criminal offence.

Title: Senior Jesuits charged with historical sex offences at Sydney’s Saint Ignatius College Riverview
Summary: One man had a senior role in Rome and the other recently served as spiritual director at the Corpus Christi seminary in Melbourne. Both will face court on Wednesday.

Title: He grabbed me like this: Girl shows court how Kyle Daniels allegedly touched her
Summary: A seven-year-old girl has stood up and pulled at the crotch of her pants to demonstrate how she says her swim coach touched her during lessons in 2019.
